data.description: Experience a one-of-a-kind property situated on a corner lot, offering a modern aesthetic with 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, and an office nestled in Ventana Lakes. Upon entering the house, you are welcomed by the spacious office. The dreamy white kitchen features 42-inch cabinets, quartz countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Next to it is the living room with high ceilings, open to below, a beautiful staircase, and numerous windows for natural sunlight.The expansive master suite boasts a separate standing walk-in shower, a bathtub, and double vanities. The second floor includes a huge game room, a movie theater, and 3 additional bedrooms—one of which is like a second master suite with a separate bathroom and a spacious closet. This floor plan is the most popular in Ventana Lakes. Located in the highly sought-after Katy ISD school district, residents enjoy access to a variety of amenities, including splash pads and pools, ensuring endless hours of entertainment and recreation.
